            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <del rend="erasure">Corneliae Sa</del><lb break="no" n="2"/><del rend="erasure">loninae sanct</del><lb break="no" n="3"/><del rend="erasure">issimae <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> con</del><lb break="no" n="4"/><del rend="erasure">iugi victorio</del><lb break="no" n="5"/><del rend="erasure">sissimi Gallie</del><lb break="no" n="6"/><del rend="erasure">ni <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> matri</del> <lb n="7"/><del rend="erasure">[castrorum sena</del>]<lb break="no" n="8"/><del rend="erasure">tus <expan><abbr>col</abbr><ex>oniae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Faliscor</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan></del> <lb n="9"/><del rend="erasure"><expan><abbr>dev</abbr><ex>otus</ex></expan> numini maies</del><lb break="no" n="10"/><del rend="erasure"><expan><abbr>tatiq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> eius curante</del> <lb n="11"/><del rend="erasure">Tyrio <expan><abbr>Sep</abbr><ex>timio</ex></expan> Azizo <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iro</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>erfectissimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>cur</abbr><ex>atore</ex></expan></del> <lb n="12"/><del rend="erasure">operum et rei <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ublicae</ex></expan></del>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die corona ist nicht erhalten. Der Text der Inschrift ist nazezu identisch mit CIL XI 3091-3092. (B): AE 1982: Kennzeichnung der Rasuren fehlt; Horster: Z. 12/13: Zeilenfall nicht angegeben. Zu Tyrius Septimius Azizus siehe auch CIL 06, 01108. 01109. add. p. 4324. Datierung: 254(?) (Erhebung Saloninas zur Augusta) bis ca. September 268 (Tod Galliens u. der Salonina).</p>
            </div>
